Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.5\fs18\fnMS PGothic\fe128}　　　…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMonotype Corsiva\fe120\fs20}SI DO RE SO…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你辦到了　路克
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們成功了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能去艾爾蘭德了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非讓這種事終結不可
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不　我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也有自己的信念

